    "description": "<p><span ><strong >Trigger:</strong> Creature you can see within 1 Space is targeted by an <strong >Attack  </strong>that targets its <strong >PD</strong>.</span></p><p><span ><strong >Reaction:</strong> You can spend <strong >1 AP</strong>Â and <strong >1 SP</strong> to become the new target of the Check, and choose to switch places with the original target (if it's willing).</span></p><p><span >If the Check is accompanied by a Save (as with a Dynamic Attack Save), you make the Save instead of the original target.</span></p><p></p><p><span ><span ><strong ><span >Technique Enhancements</span></strong></span></span></p><ul ><li ><span ><strong >Steadfast Forbearance:</strong> <strong >(1 SP)</strong> If multiple creatures within 1 Space of you (after switching places if you choose to do so) and are targeted by the same Check, you can attempt to protect them as well. You can spend<strong > 1 SP</strong> per additional target to become the new target of its Check as well. You take the collective damage of all protected creatures against the Check.</span></li><li ><span ><strong >Immense Defense: (2 SP)</strong> You gain Resistance against all damage taken using this Technique.</span></li></ul>",
